The electron transport rate (ETR) through PSII (expressed in µmol/m2 s) was calculated as4\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
