				\begin{document}$${\text{ETR}} = {{{{\Phi}}}_{{{\text{PSII}}}}} \times {\text{PPFD}} \times 0.5 \times 0.84,$$\end{document}where PPFD is the photosynthetic photon flux density (µmol/m2 s), 0.84 is the coefficient of absorption of incident light by the leaf, and 0.5 is the coefficient corresponding to even distribution of excitation energy between PSI and PSII.

The rate of CO2 net uptake was calculated from the formula5\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
